## Select field

A single select field with two display modes: Popup (Dropdown), Inline (Radio buttons)

## General options

- Field name
- Field key
- Placeholder
- Description
- Is Required
- CSS Classes
- Default value

## Specific options

- **Display as:** Popup (Dropdown), Inline (Radio buttons)
- **Choices:** Add list of choices (one per line)
